OL,3,CCovid tax repayment plans in Jersey
OL,4,Cpushed back for 26,000 people
OL,6,FPeople in Jersey who paused their
OL,7,Fprior year tax payments in 2020 have
OL,8,Fbeen given a two year extension to
OL,9,Fdecide how they will pay back their
OL,10,Foutstanding bills.
OL,12,FDuring the Covid pandemic, around #330
OL,13,Fmillion of 2019 tax liabilities were
OL,14,Ffrozen for future repayment to help
OL,15,Fsupport self-employed people and a
OL,16,Flarge proportion of employed people.
