OL,3,CCovid tax repayment plans in Jersey
OL,4,Cpushed back for 26,000 people
OL,6,FNow, Jersey's Minister for Treasury
OL,7,Fand Resources, Deputy Elaine Millar
OL,8,Fsays she will defer the start of the
OL,9,Fstatutory payment scheme for those
OL,10,Fformer 'Prior Year Basis' taxpayers,
OL,11,Ffrom 2025 to 2027.
OL,13,FDeputy Millar said: "I am pleased to
OL,14,Fannounce the deferral of the payment
OL,15,Fscheme to help islanders with the
OL,16,Fongoing concerns surrounding the cost
OL,17,Fof living.
